BBN reality TV show, Laycon showed he is also a big fan of Fecent Ricco when he danced to Fecent Ricco’s hit song ‘Joromi’ in the Big Brother House. Fecent Ricco who just dropped a remix for his hit song Simbi featured Zlatan and Guitar by Fiokee No doubt that Fecent Ricco is the new face of afrobeat and is currently working on his new EP of 4 tracks featuring top nigeria top stars. The hot Nigeria super star is in the studio working on his next big project that will drop soon. Fecent Ricco ft Zlatan & Guitar by Fiokee – Simbi (Remix) is available on all streaming platform.